<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>KALVARY LEI PANH IN CH122</title>
<key>G</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Maw zan khuamui nih ka lungthin cu a khuh, Ka retheihnak Khamhtu nih a
 hngalh, Ka lungretheih caan ah ka pawng ah a ra, Hnangamnak le daihnak a
 ka pek.

[C1]
   Kal-va-ry lei panhin kei ruangah a kal, Keimah ruangah sifah a in,
   Kalvary lei panh in kei ruangah a kal, Kei luatnak ca a thi.

[V2]
 Misual kei nih a hmaiah kun in ka biak, Pathian ngaihthiamnak ka rak
 hngal lo, Jesuh nih na sual leiba an champiak cang, Ti in aw thawng ka
 lung ah a thang.

[C2]
   Kal-va-ry lei panhin kei ruangah a kal, Keimah ruangah sifah a in,
   Kalvary lei panh in kei ruangah a kal, Kei luatnak ca a thi.

[V3]
 Khamhtu a ka dawtnak khuaruahhar a si, Sunparnak kaltak in Kal-va-ry
 ah, Serhsat phunkip ing in keimah ca a kal, A min zungzal thangthat si ko
 seh.

[C3]
   Kal-va-ry lei panhin kei ruangah a kal, Keimah ruangah sifah a in,
   Kalvary lei panh in kei ruangah a kal, Kei luatnak ca a thi.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>122</hymn_number>
</song>